des: Frenby Battery Checker skill checks for how much battery is left for Frenby. This skill only works on Frenby device. Frenby is an Alexa-enabled device developed by Infotron. It is small, light, and wearable which can be brought anywhere you want. most of the features and functionalities of Amazon Echo products still work in Frenby.
